此地下車站於1919年1月7日啟用<ref name="NYTimes Opening">{{cite web|title=New Lines In Bronx Coming This Year: Rays of Rapid Transit to be Let Into Dark Sections in the West and North|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9803E1DA1231E433A25756C0A9679C946896D6CF|website=[[紐約時報|nytimes.com]]|publisher=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|accessdate=25 January 2016|date=January 7, 1919|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220195819/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9803E1DA1231E433A25756C0A9679C946896D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>，設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和三條軌道。中央快車軌道於平日尖峰時段由[[紐約地鐵6號線|<6>號線]]列車服務。

兩個月台於1960年代在兩端分別延長，以容納[[跨區捷運公司|IRT]]標準列車長度（510英呎）。月台的延長導致車站有少許偏差。此站不設任何跨線橋或下通道。

2015－2019年[[大都會運輸署|MTA]]資金計劃中，此站與其餘30個紐約地鐵站將進行徹底重建和關閉6個月。重建包括蜂窩服務、Wi-Fi、充電站、改善指示以及車站照明<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gothamist.com/2016/01/08/subway_facelift_shutdown.php|title=MTA Will Completely Close 30 Subway Stations For Months-Long "Revamp"|publisher=Gothamist|accessdate=2016-07-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801200338/http://gothamist.com/2016/01/08/subway_facelift_shutdown.php|archivedate=2016-08-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.governor.ny.gov/sites/governor.ny.gov/files/atoms/files/MTAStations.pdf|title=MTAStations|last=|first=|date=|website=governor.ny.gov|publisher=Government of the State of New York|access-date=2016-07-18|archive-date=2019-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104021603/https://www.governor.ny.gov/sites/governor.ny.gov/files/atoms/files/MTAStations.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

